Breaking {c_important}Concealment{/c} grants {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"|%+|]{/c} Resistance and Maximum Resistance to All Elements for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 1"]{/c} seconds.

Killing an Elite enemy reduces {c_important}Concealment's{/c} Cooldown by {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|1|]{/c} seconds.
Breaking {c_important}Concealment{/c} grants Resistance. Elite kills reduce {c_important}Concealment's{/c} Cooldown by {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|1|]{/c} seconds.
